      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BOUND FOR KOS (8) will find this a little easier than his debut second two weeks ago, beaten a nose at the end of 1010m at Moruya. Sure to take a lot from that run and will prove tough to beat. LYKOS (7) missed the placings two runs back then settled well back last start when 7 lengths away in tenth over 1110m at this track. Finds the right race this time and can take this out. HABIB ALBI (2) ran very well first up then sat on the pace before fading to finish fifth last time out over 1250m at Taree. Can bounce back to his best form. AIRBURST (5) is a nine-start maiden who returned last time and finished fourth at Taree over 1250m, beaten 3.5 lengths. Will derive great benefit from that outing and deserves consideration.",
